---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="SEO Services — Hristijan Najcheski | Fractional SEO Consultant"
  description="Comprehensive SEO consulting services: Technical SEO, Content Strategy, SEO Audits, Link Building, Analytics & Reporting, Local & International SEO, and more."
  schemaType="service"
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-header-content">
        <span class="section-label">Services</span>
        <h1>SEO services that<br /><span class="text-gradient">move the needle</span></h1>
        <p>
          From technical foundations to content strategy — everything your business needs to dominate search.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Detailed Services -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="services-detailed-grid">
        <div class="service-detailed-card">
          <div class="service-icon">⚙️</div>
          <h3>Technical SEO</h3>
          <p>
            Build a technical foundation that search engines can easily crawl,
            understand, and rank. I identify and fix the issues holding your
            site back.
          </p>
          <div class="service-features">
            <span class="service-feature">Site architecture optimization</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Core Web Vitals improvement</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Crawl budget optimization</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Structured data implementation</span>
            <span class="service-feature">JavaScript SEO & rendering</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Mobile-first optimization</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-detailed-card">
          <div class="service-icon">📝</div>
          <h3>Content Strategy</h3>
          <p>
            Strategic content planning that targets the right keywords, answers
            user intent, and drives qualified organic traffic to your site.
          </p>
          <div class="service-features">
            <span class="service-feature">Keyword research & mapping</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Topic cluster strategy</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Content gap analysis</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Editorial calendar planning</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Content optimization & refresh</span>
            <span class="service-feature">E-E-A-T optimization</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-detailed-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🔍</div>
          <h3>SEO Audits</h3>
          <p>
            Comprehensive audits that uncover every opportunity and issue
            across technical, content, and off-page SEO — with a prioritized
            action plan.
          </p>
          <div class="service-features">
            <span class="service-feature">Full technical site audit</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Content quality assessment</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Backlink profile analysis</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Competitor benchmarking</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Prioritized recommendations</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Executive summary & roadmap</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-detailed-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🔗</div>
          <h3>Link Building</h3>
          <p>
            White-hat link acquisition strategies that build genuine authority
            and trust signals through high-quality, relevant backlinks.
          </p>
          <div class="service-features">
            <span class="service-feature">Digital PR & outreach</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Content-led link building</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Broken link building</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Resource page link building</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Competitor link analysis</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Toxic link disavow</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-detailed-card">
          <div class="service-icon">📊</div>
          <h3>Analytics & Reporting</h3>
          <p>
            Custom dashboards and reporting that connect SEO performance to
            business outcomes — so you always know what's working and why.
          </p>
          <div class="service-features">
            <span class="service-feature">GA4 & GSC setup & config</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Custom dashboard creation</span>
            <span class="service-feature">KPI tracking & analysis</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Conversion attribution</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Monthly performance reports</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Data-driven recommendations</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-detailed-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🌍</div>
          <h3>Local & International SEO</h3>
          <p>
            Whether you serve local markets or operate globally, I create
            strategies that reach your target audience wherever they are.
          </p>
          <div class="service-features">
            <span class="service-feature">Google Business Profile optimization</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Local citation building</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Multi-location SEO</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Hreflang implementation</span>
            <span class="service-feature">International keyword research</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Market-specific strategies</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-detailed-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🛒</div>
          <h3>E-Commerce SEO</h3>
          <p>
            Specialized SEO strategies for online stores — from product page
            optimization to category architecture and schema markup.
          </p>
          <div class="service-features">
            <span class="service-feature">Product page optimization</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Category structure strategy</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Product schema markup</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Faceted navigation handling</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Internal linking strategy</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Review & UGC optimization</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-detailed-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🚀</div>
          <h3>SEO Migration & Relaunch</h3>
          <p>
            Redesigning your site or switching platforms? I ensure your organic
            traffic is preserved and enhanced through the transition.
          </p>
          <div class="service-features">
            <span class="service-feature">Pre-migration audit</span>
            <span class="service-feature">URL mapping & redirect strategy</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Content preservation plan</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Post-migration monitoring</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Traffic recovery strategy</span>
            <span class="service-feature">Platform-specific optimization</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently asked <span class="text-gradient">questions</span></h2>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
            What does "fractional" SEO consultant mean?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              A fractional consultant works as a part-time, embedded member of your team — typically a few days per week or month. You get senior-level SEO expertise without the cost of a full-time hire, and more focused attention than you'd get from a traditional agency.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
            How long does it take to see SEO results?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              SEO is a long-term investment. Most clients start seeing meaningful improvements in 3-6 months, with compounding returns over time. Quick wins from technical fixes can show impact within weeks, while content and link strategies build momentum over months.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
            What industries do you work with?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              I've worked across SaaS, e-commerce, publishing, healthcare, finance, real estate, and more. SEO principles are universal — what changes is the strategy and competitive landscape. I adapt my approach to each industry's unique challenges.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
            How do you measure success?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Success is measured through agreed-upon KPIs that tie back to business goals — organic traffic growth, keyword rankings, conversion rates, revenue from organic search, and more. I provide transparent monthly reports so you always know where things stand.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
            What's your engagement model?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              I offer flexible engagement models: retainer-based fractional consulting (ongoing), project-based work (audits, migrations), and advisory/mentorship. We'll find the model that best fits your needs and budget during our initial conversation.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <h2>Need a custom <span class="text-gradient-orange">SEO solution</span>?</h2>
        <p>
          Every business is unique. Let's discuss your specific challenges and build a strategy that works for you.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-orange btn-lg">Let's Talk →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
